#|==================================================================================|#
#|==================================================================================|#
#| Syntax      | Meaning                                                        	|#
#| ----------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- 	|#
#|  filename   | Ignores a file in the root or any subdirectory (e.g., `*.log`) 	|#
#|  folder/    | Ignores an entire directory and everything inside it, recursively	|#
#|  *.ext      | Ignores all files with the .ext extension, anywhere 		     	|#
#|  **/file    | Ignores `file` in any subdirectory (all directories,recursive)   	|#
#|  !filename  | **Negates** a rule: includes a file previously ignored         	|#
#|  /filename  | Ignores a file only in the root directory of the repository    	|#
#|==================================================================================|#



